subject: Second Chance - Free Viewing of Zurawski v Texas
body: I HIGHLY recommend you watch this documentary this weekend. View this email inyour browser (https://mailchi.mp/987033b5a265/amanda-zurawski-vs-texas-12709419?e=ebba716312) https://www.theresa4texas.com Hi Friend, ** Ifyou didn't get a chance to watch the documentary, Zurawski v Texas, I HIGHLYrecommend you watch it this weekend.------------------------------------------------------------ ** The Center forReproductive Rights sums it up:------------------------------------------------------------ "In the newdocumentary feature film Zurawski v Texas, independent filmmakers Maisie Crowand Abbie Perrault show the stark and terrifying reality of what it means tobe pregnant in a U.S. state that has banned abortion—and the bravery, grit anddetermination that it takes to speak out. Crow and Perrault followed threeTexas women who were denied medically necessary abortion care—Amanda Zurawski,Samantha Casiano, and Dr. Austin Dennard—as they brought their stories andbattled their case up to the Texas Supreme Court, with the help of the Centerfor Reproductive Rights’ Senior Staff Attorney Molly Duane." Watch Zurawski vTexas for free Nov 2 and 3 here(https://watch.eventive.org/togetherfilms/play/670db1d13a247100e803df13/670db1dc3f8905002cc42691)** If you are able to give, I am sure the Center for Reproductive Rights coulduse your donation.------------------------------------------------------------ Donate the theCenter for Reproductive Rights here (https://reproductiverights.org/) Theyhave cases across the country and could use our support while they fightagainst the extreme abortion bans that put women's lives in jeopardy. ** Ifyou haven't voted yet, today is the last day of early voting and Tuesday isElection Day. ------------------------------------------------------------Thanks for your help. ** Onwards,------------------------------------------------------------ ** Theresa------------------------------------------------------------ Donate(https://secure.actblue.com/donate/abrighterfuturefortexas) Volunteer(https://www.theresa4texas.com/get-involved) Issues(https://www.theresa4texas.com/what-theresa-stands-for) Shop(https://store.theresa4texas.com) https://www.theresa4texas.com Follow me onsocial media - and share with your friends and family!https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61552530122152https://www.instagram.com/theresa4texas https://www.twitter.com/theresa4texashttps://tiktok.com/theresa4texashttps://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyd_ZE7lgKTjDchvDRg4A9g Pol.
